gomodel:SYNGO_261  a      owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: >10fold-enriched in docked SV fraction (fig. 5)\n\n20/3/2017 Pim\n- Because enriched in AZ and not in free SV protein is presumably localized to the AZ, and not in co-purifying SVs.\n-According to uniprot Flot-2 has a lipid anchor justifying the \"anchored component of ....\" term.. Experimental description: Results: \"To isolate docking complexes from **rat brain**, we first prepared synaptosomes and subjected them to limited proteolysis to dissociate pre- and postsynaptic membranes (Figure 1A).\"" , "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099029 replaced by GO:0048787" ;
